snippet.title: Monster Hunter Rise: Sunbreak - Announce Trailer | Xbox Series X|S, Xbox One, Windows, PS5, PS4
snippet.description:
The Kingdom calls for new Hunters! Sunbreak, the massive expansion to Monster Hunter Rise comes to Xbox Series X|S, Xbox One, Windows, PS5, and PS4 on April 28!  

Step up to Master Rank and hunt your way through a mysterious new story. New monsters, locales, gear, and an expansive endgame await!

Monster Hunter Rise is now available on Xbox Series X|S, Xbox One, Windows, Game Pass, PS5, and PS4.

Pre-order Monster Hunter Rise: Sunbreak!
Microsoft Store: https://www.xbox.com/en-us/games/store/monster-hunter-rise-sunbreak/9njc9v791cq1
PlayStation Store: https://store.playstation.com/en-us/product/UP0102-PPSA08033_00-MASSIVEEXPANSION

Buy Monster Hunter Rise now! 
Microsoft Store: https://www.xbox.com/en-us/games/store/monster-hunter-rise/9n1vp8wdqk4d
PlayStation Store: https://bit.ly/MHRise_PS

Learn more about Monster Hunter Rise: 
https://www.monsterhunter.com/rise-xwp/

#MonsterHunter #MHRise #capcom
